OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOver four million illegal  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fvapes seized at border     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of illegal vapes seized at  
OL,6, the border quadrupled last year as UK  
OL,7, authorities wrestle with unlicensed    
OL,8, imports amid a surge in youth vaping.  
OL,10,FMore than 4.5m vapes weighing nearly   
OL,11,Ften tonnes were seized over the last 12
OL,12,Fmonths, four times more than 2022.     
OL,14,FThe figures were released to the BBC   
OL,15,Fafter a Freedom of Information (FOI)   
OL,16,Frequest.                               
OL,18,FThe government is soon to announce new 
OL,19,Frules for the industry, including a    
OL,20,Fpossible ban on disposable vapes.      
